      <title>韩国医生投票决定 6 月 18 日罢工，抗议改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/korean-doctors-vote-to-strike-on-june-18-in-protest-over-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国最大的医生组织投票赞成于 6 月 18 日举行罢工，这是该组织首次采取集体行动抗议政府的医疗行业改革计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/korean-doctors-vote-to-strike-on-june-18-in-protest-over-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 08:40:06 GMT</pubDate>
